\begin_inset Formula $ensembles(1)$
\end_inset

 is the size of the ensemble of trajectories computed in each processor.
 Once data is averaged internally over 
\begin_inset Formula $ensembles(1)$
\end_inset

, further transforms of the resulting averages are available.
